<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-03-0959 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper investigates the mutual dependence of a utility's power gridand its nuclear power stations. This interdependence can be summarizedas follows: the grid must be a reliable source of power to the system'snuclear power stations; the nuclear power plant network must be a reliablesource of power to the grid. The important role which nuclear power playsin the French power system has made both of these principles - the secondin particular - of vital interest to EDF power system engineers.</TEXT></DOC>